blocks.content:
Welcome to Alphonso's Choice, where the rich tapestry of Dutch craftsmanship meets the universal language of fashion.

Our story

Nestled amidst the picturesque canals and cobbled streets of Amsterdam, Alphonso's Choice was conceived by JMango360 B.V. in 2023. Inspired by the vibrant mix of cultures, art, and history of The Netherlands, our brand embodies the essence of Amsterdam - a harmonious blend of tradition and modernity.

The vision behind the Brand

At the heart of Alphonso's Choice is an aspiration to craft pieces that resonate with timeless grace while echoing contemporary trends. We draw from the meticulous attention to detail synonymous with Dutch artistry, infusing every design with a hint of the unexpected.

Sustainability and craftsmanship

In the land of windmills, bicycles, and eco-conscious living, sustainability isn’t just a buzzword – it’s a way of life. Alphonso's Choice proudly incorporates this ethos. Our pieces are crafted from eco-friendly materials, and we employ sustainable practices from design to delivery, ensuring that our footprint on the environment is minimal.

The Alphonso's essence

Our brand name, 'Alphonso's Choice', is more than just a label. It signifies a curated selection of the finest, handpicked with discerning taste and an eye for unparalleled style. Every item is a nod to the sartorial elegance of those who wish to express themselves without words.

The Dutch connection

Being rooted in Amsterdam gives us a unique perspective on global fashion. The Dutch are known for their straightforwardness, innovation, and a keen eye for quality. We channel these attributes into every collection, offering fashion-forward pieces that don't compromise on durability and comfort.

Join the Alphonso's community

We invite you to be a part of the Alphonso's Choice family, a community that embraces the spirit of Amsterdam - progressive, artistic, and ever-evolving.

Thank you for choosing Alphonso's Choice, a testament to Dutch ingenuity and global aesthetics.

Privacy policy

 

 

Last updated September 12, 2023

Thank you for choosing to be a part of our community at Alphonso's Choice, a brand under JMango360 B.V. Protecting your privacy is crucial to us. This Privacy Policy outlines our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of your information through https://alphonso-choice.mybigcommerce.com/ ("the Website").

1. Information we collect

  • Personal information: Direct information such as your name, email address, shipping/billing address, phone number, payment details, and any other data you provide when registering or making a purchase.
  • Usage data: Information about how you interact with our Website, including visited pages, time and date of access, time spent, and other diagnostic data.
  • Cookies & tracking data: To enhance your experience, we use cookies and similar tracking technologies.

2. Use of your information

  • Order processing: To process and fulfill your orders.
  • Personalization: To tailor your experience on our Website.
  • Updates & communication: To send periodic emails regarding your orders or other products and services.
  • Analysis: For internal analytics to improve our offerings.
  • Security: To protect the security and integrity of our Website.

3. Sharing of information

  • Service providers: We collaborate with third-party companies and individuals to enhance our Website, and these providers have access to your Personal Data only to perform these tasks and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.
  • Compliance with laws: In case of legal obligations, we might disclose your data.
  • Business transfers: If we undergo a merger or acquisition, your information may be transferred.

4. Your choices and rights

  • Access & correction: You can access, update, or delete your personal information directly within your account settings or by contacting us.
  • Cookies: You can instruct your browser to refuse cookies or notify you when a cookie is being sent.

5. Security measures

We strive to use commercially acceptable methods to protect your personal data. However, no electronic storage method or data transmission over the Internet is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

6. External links

Our Website may contain links to external sites not operated by us. If you click on these links, you will be directed to third-party websites. We strongly advise reviewing the Privacy Policy of every site you visit.

7. Children’s privacy

Our Website is not targeted at individuals under 13 years. We do not knowingly collect personal data from anyone under 13 years of age.

8. Changes to this privacy policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page, and, if significant, we will provide a more prominent notice (including email notification).

9. Contact us

If you have any concerns or questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@jmango360.com

Thank you for placing your trust in Alphonso's Choice. We value and respect your privacy.

IN-STORE PICKUP

  • FREE
  • Barbara Strozzilaan 201, Amsterdam 1083 HN, Netherlands (9AM - 6PM, Mon - Fri)

LOCAL SHIPPING

  • Delivery in 2-5 business days after dispatch
  • FREE shipping on every order over €200 without discount code

INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING

  • Delivery in 5-15 business days after dispatch
  • FREE shipping on every order over €300 without discount code

RETURNS: You have 30 days from the date of receipt to return an item. 

EXCHANGES: If you need an exchange for the same item, send us an email at support@jmango360.com with details and photos if applicable.

blocks.content:
Shipping

We can ship to virtually any address in the world. Note that there are restrictions on some products, and some products cannot be shipped to international destinations.

When you place an order, we will estimate shipping and delivery dates for you based on the availability of your items and the shipping options you choose. Depending on the shipping provider you choose, shipping date estimates may appear on the shipping quotes page.

Please also note that the shipping rates for many items we sell are weight-based. The weight of any such item can be found on its detail page. To reflect the policies of the shipping companies we use, all weights will be rounded up to the next full pound.
